name: COMING SOON!! Keep The Boobies Bouncing © STICKER
description:
***This product will be available SOON!***

ALL PROFIT will be going to help our dear friend JoEllen Fetterhoff, to help with the costs that cancer can cause. 
In May of 2012, JoEllen was diagnosed with breast cancer. JoEllen is 28 years old, and has a beautiful 5 year old daughter.

JoEllen has been a big part of many cancer fundraisers and cancer awareness events- specifically annual events facilitated by Melinda Dollhopf (of Live Life Events) where DJs like Crisco Kidd helped bring awareness through the love of music. This design (created by That Girl Amber) was made to reflect those special events, and to show our love and support for JoEllen and her family through this hard time.

This t-shirt has a relaxed but tailored fit. The seamless rib collar with double-needle cover-stitching, shoulder to shoulder taping, double-needle sleeve and bottom hem make it a durable wear. Made from 100% pre-shrunk cotton with a fabric weight of 6.1 oz.

All designs © That Girl Amber- Photo & Design, 2001 - 2012
